channel.title: Ram
channel.description:
Ram
Well, yesterday, I started to get pissed with my computer lagging for like 5 mins after boot. So, I purchased some new ram off Trade Me.
http://www.trademe.co.nz/Browse/Listing.aspx?id=185080824
Price: $26.01NZD, $12USD Speed: DDR2 800 Size: 2GB Age: Brand new
Is that a good price? Don't tell me that I should have got 2x1gb, cause my Mobo craps out with it. It lets me boot once, then I need to reset the BIOS.
